        <name>LayerUpdateProc</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Function signature for a Layer&apos;s render callback (the name of the type is derived from the words &apos;update procedure&apos;). The system will call the <computeroutput>.update_proc</computeroutput> callback whenever the Layer needs to be rendered. </para>
        </briefdescription>
